# Comment stickiness through sort: comments travel with their block.
# Per spec/02-formatting.md, the example illustrates that sorting reorders blocks
# (A1 before A2) and brings each block's attached comments along.

activity A0 "x" {
    I1 "in"

    # below A2 — sticks to A2 (no blank between)

    # above A1 — sticks to A1 (no blank between)
    A1 "first"     : I1 -> X11 "z"
    A2 "second"    : I1 -> X21 "y"
}
